parameters:
Hinata Aki: Why did you call me out to a place like this? What
do you want to talk about?
Hinata Aki: Huh...? Wait... what's this?

Hinata Aki: Souta...!... Do you really think it's okay to do
something like this!?

Sota: But... when I see Aki-neechan, I get all flustered...
that's why... I couldn't help it.

Hinata Aki: J-Just because of that, it doesn't mean you can do
whatever you want...
Sota: Please... Aki-neechan, I'm begging you.
Sota: ...Show me your breasts, without any clothes on.
Hinata Aki: A-Are you an idiot?! What's gotten into you, Sota...

Hinata Aki: Take a moment to cool your head... and make sure to
delete that photo!
Sota: \{ Hey everyone! I managed to get this kind of photo!
Hinata Aki: \{Hey, hey! Cut it out!!!
Hinata Aki: What are you trying to show off! Geez!!
Sota: ...Because she won't show me her breasts.
Hinata Aki: No breasts!... But well... if it's a bra...
Hinata Aki: (Sigh... What am I saying...)

Sota: A bra, huh... But if I can see them without it, I guess
it's fine...!
Hinata Aki: Sigh... When did I become like this...
Sota: It's different from the bra in the photo!
Sota: Even if you say that in that outfit, it doesn't scare me.
Sota: They're way bigger than Mom's!

Sota: Have you already shown this side to \P[0001]-niichan?
Like, in this outfit...
Hinata Aki: Huh...? No... It's not like that with \P[0001]...
Sota: Seriously?! So, am I the first one?
Sota: Hehe... I did it... I'm Aki-neechan's first~!
Hinata Aki: Hey... Don't say it in a weird way! Geez!

Hinata Aki: I've shown you enough... so don't do anything weird
anymore.
Perhaps it's because Sota always treats me like a child...
I didn't really feel embarrassed or anything like that.
But it's said that Sota was looking at me with a lewd gaze...
I felt a strong sense of discomfort and it made me feel weird...
Happy-looking child: Swings are definitely the most fun!

Sota's friend:
 I found a stag beetle earlier! Isn't it cool!
Calm child: Big brother, you seem unlucky.

Muddy child: I'm going to work hard and learn how to do a
backflip!
